# Requirements #
- board:
    + _OK_ power supply 12v
    + _OK_ 4 channel pwm 8bit
    + _OK_ bus addresable
- hardware:
    + _NX_ 1/8 unit load RS485 driver
    + _OK_ led debug
    + _OK_ led prog
    + _OK_ high side power stage 1.5A nominal per channel
    + _NX_ configurable constant current
    + _OK_ MCU based
- software:
    + _OK_ address programable via EUSART (non volatile)
    + precission DMX reader routine
    + fading output / smooth changes
- load:
    + _OK_ closed loop load

